{"id":282392,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/【图说天朝】3-04案件报道要求/","date":"2013-03-06T01:07:52Z","modified":"2013-03-06T01:07:52Z","title":"【图说天朝】3.04案件报道要求","content":"<p>5日，吉林省长春婴儿被盗案嫌犯自首（婴儿被杀）后，吉林省有关媒体接到省市级报道要求，有媒体人将截图发布于网络。报道要求，媒体不得炒作此事，并且要注重舆论引导“传递正能量”，不得指责公安办案能力，不得渲染悲情&#8230;&#8230;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_282393\" style=\"width: 609px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/BEnBWK2CQAICEHD.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-282393\" alt=\"BEnBWK2CQAICEHD\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/BEnBWK2CQAICEHD.jpg\" width=\"599\" height=\"384\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/BEnBWK2CQAICEHD.jpg 599w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/BEnBWK2CQAICEHD-300x192.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">网传图片，发布者不详。</p></div>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18269,10466,21627,13770],"tags":[22454,22460,21038,28510,20928]}